{
  "stem": "3721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, with these papers, I would be able to get, get around quite well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a sidearm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had the whole uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had my birth certificate and then everything with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would be able to go around in Budapest quite well, no, no hindrance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even some of the Hungarian-- by the way, I forgot to mention, I think around September the 15th, very soon after, the-- that Lakatos government was overthrown by a Nazi quiddling again, a very-- they were mainly the, the Arrow Cross-- the most vicious Nazis that they could have.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, they were already shooting people on the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they caught you, you were a Jew-- and so we really intervened in many cases because we were the-- as Hungarian soldiers, we were a group of three people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of them was actually from, I think, from Kolozsvar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His name was Loevy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But his mother was an ethnic German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was very blond and really, the most Aryan-looking individual you could ever see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was another guy whose name I somehow can't remember now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's one of the things that I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we, as a group, were going around Budapest, and wherever we saw trouble with these Arrow Cross-- they were a bunch of hooligans that wound up with machine guns and, and hand guns, brand new ones, from the German arsenal that arrived to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And their purpose in life was only one thing-- to kill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And kill-- mainly kill Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sometimes by mistake, they killed their own, because they would accuse some people that you are a Jew, and shoot them on place without asking.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they wound up to be not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It happened many cases, many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
